Three People Have Perished And More Than 20 Injured Along The Malindi?Mombasa Highway Mida Area In A Grisly Accident Involving A 14 Seater Matatu And A Private Vehicle On Saturday Night. According To Police And Eye Witness Accounts, The Private Vehicle, A Toyota Wish, Was Over Speeding When It Collided Head On With The Matatu. One Passenger Died On The Spot And Two Others Succumbed To Injuries After Being Rushed To Malindi Sub County Hospital. Survivors Of The Crash Sustained Fractures And Head Injuries.